{"about_the_game":"Bonfire and Tail is a multiplayer action party game developed by avidya studio.<br>The original idea of the game is to get back to childhood together with our players, leaving behind troubles and worries, and try to embrace the pure fun we had when we were children. <br>The game features a light rhythm, a simple and bright style. Cute little furies accompanied by a warm campfire to illuminate the young hearts of every player.<br>Bonfire and tail includes a dozen mini games. All of them are easy, fun and thrilling, have at it and enjoy!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/GamPlayGIF2.gif?t=1694257739\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/GamPlayGIF4.gif?t=1694257739\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/GamPlayGIF6.gif?t=1694257739\" /><br>In order to secure victory, you need to ignite the opposing player's tail to gain points. Players with an ignited tail would have to keep wiggling their tails to extinguish the flame.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/GamPlayGIF1.gif?t=1694257739\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/GamPlayGIF5.gif?t=1694257739\" /><br>Characters and map designs will be added in upcoming patches.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/GamPlayGIF3.gif?t=1694257739\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/\u5730\u56fe\u5c55\u793a55.gif?t=1694257739\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/\u5730\u56fe\u5c55\u793a66.gif